<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>mdat view — build the frontend first</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; background: #0a0a0a; color: #e5e5e5; margin: 2rem; line-height: 1.5; }
      code { background: #1a1a1a; padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; }
      h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>mdat view</h1>
    <p>The frontend bundle has not been built yet.</p>
    <p>
      Run <code>cd crates/mdat-view/web &amp;&amp; bun install &amp;&amp; bun run build</code>
      (or <code>npm install &amp;&amp; npm run build</code>), then rebuild the binary.
    </p>
    <p>
      Until then, the API at <code>/&lt;token&gt;/dataset</code> and
      <code>/&lt;token&gt;/plane</code> still works.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>